   <http://omv.ontoware.org/2005/05/ontology#keywords> "marine observatorier, FAIR-data, EMSO, forskningsinfrastrukturer, ontologi, undervannsobservatorier"@no ,
                                                       "marine observatories, FAIR data, EMSO, research infrastructures, ontology, underwater observatories"@en ,
                                                       "observatoare marine, date FAIR, EMSO, infrastructuri de cercetare, ontologie, observatoare subacvatice"@ro ,
                                                       "observatoires marins, données FAIR, EMSO, infrastructures de recherche, ontologie, observatoires sous-marins"@fr ,
