###  https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#dateEndDeployment
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#dateEndDeployment> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ;
                                                        rdfs:subPropertyOf <http://schema.org/endDate> ;
