###  https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Black_Sea
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Black_Sea> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                                         <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> ;
                                                <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility_is_linked_to_a_project> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#EUXINUS> ;
                                                <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#containsSite> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#EuxRo01> ,
                                                                                                   <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#EuxRo02> ,
                                                                                                   <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#EuxRo03> ;
                                                <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#hasBoundingBox> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Black_Sea_RF_bbox> ;
                                                <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#hasERICMembership> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Black_Sea_EMSO_membership> ;
                                                <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#hasRegionalTeamLeader> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Vlad_Rădulescu> ;
                                                <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ledByOrganization> <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#GeoEcoMar> ;
